<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>mnạl smyr, mnạl smyr</author>
<hymn_number>233</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bạʿtrf qdạmk yạ yswʿ ạlmsyḥ
 ạ̹ny mạstḥqsẖ dmạʾ ạldẖbyḥ
 sạlt ʿlsẖạny wạlṣlyb fdạny
 ạ̉nạ rạjʿ lyk bqlby ạljryḥ
 ạlqrạr- twbẗ mn qlby ạlly tạh ʿnk bʿyd
 twbẗ mn qlby lfạdy ạlwḥyd
 wạnt zmạn yạmạ kẖbṭt ʿly̱ bạby
 ạlnhạrdh yạ rby hạftḥ qlby wạ̉bwạby
 2- bạʿtrf qdạmk bqsạwẗ qlby
 wạlkẖṭyẗ sạdt wạnạ sẖạyf dẖnby
 wbrgẖm ạlkẖṭyẗ bậjy bạlly fyã
 ạ̹qblny ạ̉nạ rạjʿ btwbẗ qlby</lyrics>
<title>bạʿtrf qdạmk</title>
</song>